#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\note{8}{\n"
"  Having a \\svgunit{golden} Dwelling built in your Town allows you to draw an \\svgunit{azure} Unit Card using the basic (top) effect of a Diplomacy Ability Card.\n"
